                            <comment id="12620840" author="mahadev" created="Fri, 8 Aug 2008 06:21:00 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;my mistake. &lt;img class=&quot;emoticon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/emoticons/smile.gif&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt; I shouldnt have committed it without a test.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
